ir, er det ikke tvil om. De har betydelige tillegg til grunnl\u00f8nnen. Det mener jeg n\u00e5 at Norwegian har dokumentert, sier Sk\u00e5nvik."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "9091e8e17950b415420bb4119515ed9e32e4243deae0e37a077288f411ff1e69"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-02T12:42:22.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Av de 100 best betalte i lavprisselskapet Norwegian er det 93 piloter."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8425177.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/afp000604410-LMUCqUn1cV.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b8c2210dbaeca3f5192afcaf535a3ed8c050f3ac.jpg?5988ed07"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Norwegian gir ut toppl\u00f8nnsliste i kamp mot pilotene -adressa.no", "93 av 100 er piloter", "Feil, mener pilotlederen", "Pilotens l\u00f8nnsoversikt", "Svarer p\u00e5 angrep"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b8c2210dbaeca3f5192afcaf535a3ed8c050f3ac"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "travel"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["best betalte", "pilot"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["aftenposten", "dreamliner", "norwegian", "anne-sissel sk\u00e5nvik"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "spania"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["bj\u00f8rn kjos", "halvor vatnar", "asgeir nyseth", "frode foss"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "o